    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Applied decorative works made of cast paste or gesso applied to wooden moldings. Use pastiglia for works designed using the application of a mould. For works designed using free-hand brush application, use "aggetti."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
